message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's worth more than $120 to me, and I believe it could be very valuable to you as well. Considering its quality and benefits, I would like to propose a price of $150 for it. Let me know if this works for you or if you'd like to make a counteroffer.
I appreciate your offer, but I'm looking to save some money. I'm willing to pay $125 for the product. I think it's a fair price considering its value to me.
